  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Build your army, battle your enemies and become a master of Spinjitzu as you recover powerful ninja weapons and restore the world's harmony in LEGO Battles: Ninjago! Deploy Hero troops through exciting missions and adventures to defeat the sinister Skulkin forces, play as the bad guys and face-off against ninjas of Spinjitzu, or challenge a friend in thrilling multiplayer battles to see whose army ranks supreme.",
